videos.description: Luke Maye takes the rebound, runs the floor and finishes the and-1 layup.
videos.headline: Maye's one-man fast-break leads to and-1

videos.description: Jericole Hellems throws a pass behind his head to an open DJ Funderburk for the slam.
videos.headline: NC State's sweet pass leads to easy dunk

videos.description: Garrison Brooks pump fakes, then slides in for a big dunk.
videos.headline: UNC's Brooks pumps, throws down big slam

videos.description: After North Carolina's Coby White misses his shot, UNC's Garrison Brooks cleans up the play with an electric dunk.
videos.headline: Brooks throws down powerful dunk
